There are indication that Peter Obi would be visiting Kaduna state soon. Peter obi happens to be one of the presidential aspirants of the forthcoming elections, as he would contest under the umbrella of the People’s Democratic Party.
However, reacting to the recent report of Peter Obi visiting Kaduna state, Former Nigerian senator, Senator Shehu Sani released a statement via his verified twitter handle.
In his statement he stated, “Peter Obi is coming to Kaduna; As a good friend, any proverb said in Hausa or Fulani or Arabic dialects, I will help in translating it and send to your Whatsapp, so that they don’t give you the Jagaban—Ameachi experience by the time you leave.
Below is a screenshot of Senator Shehu Sani’s statement gotten from his verified twitter handle;What do you have to say about this statement from senator Shehu Sani to Peter Obi?


